{"tid":39632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜特蒂憶當年 騎重機親上街頭掃毒","createTime":"2016-12-14T16:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T16:47:41.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff64cbd01ec4802d24d90d80dc1ed192fd9254e2","tid":39632,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"（中央社記者林行健馬尼拉14日專電）菲律賓總統杜特蒂向1群商界人士說，他在南部納卯市擔任市長期間，喜歡騎重型機車親自上街頭掃毒。<br />\n<br />\n「菲律賓每日詢問者報」（Philippine Daily Inquirer）今天報導，杜特蒂於12日晚間在總統府馬拉坎南宮主持1場商務論壇時說，他昔日在納卯市常騎重機巡視街頭，尋找犯罪分子。<br />\n<br />\n杜特蒂在為警方掃毒殺戮辯解時說，「我不是在自誇，在納卯市，我曾親自動手，向警察以身作則，我能，你為什麼不能？」<br />\n<br />\n他繼續說，「我騎重機巡視納卯市，我在街頭巡邏，尋找槍戰的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n這篇標題為「杜特蒂：我曾親手殺毒嫌」的報導說，當時納卯市犯罪行為氾濫，有「謀殺之都」之稱，杜特蒂以這樣的手法打擊犯罪，時代雜誌因此於2002年封他「制裁者」的外號。<br />\n<br />\n杜特蒂強調，他不會因國內外人權人士的抨擊而停止掃毒行動，「你要逮捕我、推翻我？來啊。暗殺我啊，反正我每天都為偏頭痛所苦。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，杜特蒂剛在不久前的模範青年頒獎活動上說，他不是殺人魔，殺人並不會為他帶來快樂。<br />\n<br />\n有人權人士建議應把吸毒者送進戒毒所，而不是殺掉，杜特蒂回應，國家的戒毒設施不足，有意見的人「何不把自己的家讓出1、2間房作戒毒所？或是認養毒蟲？」<br />\n<br />\n杜特蒂的言論經常引發爭議，馬拉坎南宮官員曾向媒體表示，要懂得區別他何時是在開玩笑，何時是在說真話。1051214<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20161214/983363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20161214%2F983363.jpg&h=13d140ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201612140158-1.aspx?utm_source=facebook.com&amp;utm_medium=fanpage&amp;utm_campaign=fbpost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201612140158-1.aspx%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook.com%26utm_medium%3Dfanpage%26utm_campaign%3Dfbpost&d=Z9oVvM%2FKQPLTnR4gBvc82nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5520a2d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201612140158-1.aspx?utm_source=facebook.com&amp;utm_medium=fanpage&amp;utm_campaign=fbpost</a>"},{"pid":"6715cdbcf5770e3287f2e2cc4a795a61cc8c7a4f","tid":39632,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"咁癲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673a9312ebbce06d0937e647a749820ce390e30b","tid":39632,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"唔夠戒毒所就可以就地政法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4145fa5aeba006a100c36d7980a5fc2f6383b2ac","tid":39632,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f294e1fe0f0839ccaa1e453b7cb1c4ec4ddf84a","tid":39632,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"trump係扮癲吸癲佬票，<br />\n肚凸耳凸係真係癲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}